how do i get my kids back on sims pc open for business yo i'm playing sims open for business and all of my kids just got taken away they're all children and two of them are twins boy and girl and the other one is a girl i'm pretty upset is there a cheat code or something a way to get them back there is a way they won't be exactly related anymore but you can get them back into your house go to another household and get them to adopt all children taken away go into a pool of adoptable children your children will be top of the list and will be the first ones to come when you choose to adopt once you've got all your kids in the new household save and exit this house and go back to their original family house you have to do it this way as sims that have had children taken away will not be able to adopt invite the children over this is why you need them in another house when they arrive the rest is simple boolprop testingcheatsenabled true shift and click on your sim choose spawn then tombstone of l and d on the tombstone select add to family this will give you a list of all sims on the lot that aren't in your household select the child's name do this for each of your children and congratulations you have your children back they will still be related to the household that adopted them but they'll stay in your household and can be raised as if they were The Sims 2 The Sims The Brady Bunch The Sims 2: University Pools of Darkness The Inside EastEnders Eddie Guerrero Gradius Cliff Richard Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an P.O.O.L. Highway 61 Revisited Operation: G.R.O.W.U.P.: Getting Really Old Will Upset Plans Poker jargon The Sims 2: Nightlife Counter-Strike Adoption Quicksort Pi-calculus Peter Pan Perfect Dark Aerial (dance move) Family name Bish__jo game Minesweeper (computer game) Shawn Michaels Expansion pack Big Brother (USA TV series) RuneScape quests Pitaten Empire Burlesque History of computer and video games One Tree Hill (TV series) 1987 World Series 